{"tid":2201984,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"梁國雄2016年立法會搶文件案 申請上訴至終院被潘兆初、林文瀚、彭偉昌拒絕","createTime":"2020-09-14T08:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T09:24:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6c15d8d62639309b2fea08e1d68b56a16b37ac18","tid":2201984,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T08:34:53.000Z","msg":"立法會前議員梁國雄在2016年立法會搶文件案，被控違反《立法會(權力及特權)條例》的藐視罪，裁判官裁定相關條文不適用於檢控議員，律政司其後上訴得直，上庭訴將案件發還重審。梁國雄申請上訴至終審法院，今日被上訴庭拒絕批出上訴許可。<br />\n<br />\n上訴庭認為，梁國雄一方只是重覆早前已被上訴庭拒絕接納的論點，亦並非合理爭論。判詞指，立法會有權處罰違反《條例》中藐視罪的立法會議員，同時亦可以在律政司司長批准下，控告該名議員，由法庭作出處罰，又指有關條例是適用於立法會議員，以額外保障立法會內部紀律處分權，若只適用於公眾，條文應該會列明清楚。<br />\n<br />\n法庭提到，即使《立法會(權力及特權)條例》保障立法會程序期間的絕對言論自由及辯論，亦保障不到干犯《條例》中藐視罪的行為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549530-20200914.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549530-20200914.htm&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8E9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=3466ebda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549530-20200914.htm&h=4da02e55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549530-20200914.htm</a>"},{"pid":"57a037d7329df630c36f224688b047f417de86e7","tid":2201984,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T08:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba4f3618eec59713c73a72ab5764f7d4df144565","tid":2201984,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57a037d7329df630c36f224688b047f417de86e7","tid":2201984,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T08:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\